        {
          "reviewTitle": "Just the right coverage and has your skin covered",
          "reviewText": "This is an excellent foundation with SPF. I used it for a cruise I went on, the coverage is just enough, however, it is buildable. Just like any other sunscreen, you need to reapply every few hours, and I used a powder SPF on top while out in the sun all day. My face stays put and protected from the sun. I usually use a light medium, and I purchased this in Medium. It is a great beige color to match my skin. The consistency is like regular foundation and melts into the skin without feeling heavy. I have dry skin, and I do not feel oily at all.",
