        {
          "reviewTitle": "It's BACK & BETTER! YAY!",
          "reviewText": "I love this SPF foundation from Laura Geller. It was gone for a while, and I had one heck of a time trying to find something I liked in its place. But now it's back and I can forget about all those lesser products. I use it as my all over face base, and then apply the rest of my makeup on top. It's very good quality, glides on well, and protects my fair skin from the sun. It doesn't make me greasy, it doesn't make me dry, it's just perfect. Thank you so much for bringing it back!",
